# Flutter & Dart

```toon
rules[9]{id,rule}:
1	Use debugPrint not print
2	No hardcoded business rules/mock data; prefer dynamic/API-based solutions
3	Prefer const constructors, list literals, map literals
4	Line length 120 (unless project overrides to 80)
5	Use package: imports, never relative for lib files
6	Never edit generated files (*.g.dart *.freezed.dart *.mocks.dart GeneratedPluginRegistrant.*)
7	Comment only non-obvious side effects or hidden logic; no comments on barrel/export files
8	Tests follow AAA (Arrange-Act-Assert)
9	Monorepo commits: Conventional Commits type(package_name): desc; scope=nearest pubspec.yaml; max 80 chars; imperative mood; no bullets; prefer small commits
```
